<topic id="xsd-rng-quick-fixes">
  <title>Quick Fixes for DTD, XSD, and Relax NG Errors</title>
      <body>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> offers <xref keyref="glossentry_quick-fix"><term>Quick
        Fixes</term></xref> for common errors that appear in XML documents that are validated
      against DTD, XSD, or Relax NG schemas.<note>For XML documents validated against XSD schemas,
        the <term>Quick Fixes</term> are only available if you use the default Xerces validation
        engine.</note>
      <term>Quick Fixes</term> are available in <uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> mode <ph
        product="author editor authorEclipse editorEclipse">and <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol>
        mode</ph>.</p>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> provides <term>Quick Fixes</term> for numerous types of problems,
      including the following:<table frame="all" id="simpletable_ovw_q4g_3r" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="1.0*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1.16*"/>
          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry>Problem Type</entry>
              <entry>Available Quick Fixes</entry>
            </row>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry>A specific element is required in the current context</entry>
              <entry>Insert the required element</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>An element is invalid in the current context</entry>
              <entry>Remove the invalid element</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>The content of the element should be empty</entry>
              <entry>Remove the element content</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>An element is not allowed to have child elements</entry>
              <entry>Remove all child elements</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>Text is not allowed in the current element</entry>
              <entry>Remove the text content</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>A required attribute is missing</entry>
              <entry>Insert the required attribute</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>An attribute is not allowed to be set for the current element</entry>
              <entry>Remove the attribute</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>The attribute value is invalid</entry>
              <entry>Propose the correct attribute values</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>ID value is already defined</entry>
              <entry>Generate a unique ID value</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>References to an invalid ID</entry>
              <entry>Change the reference to an already defined ID</entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table></p>
  </body>
